  "overallPacing": "非常に速いペースで、次々と驚きの絵画と視聴者の反応が切り替わる。短いテロップとAI音声でテンポ良く進行する。",
  "narrationStyle": "AI読み上げ風・短文テロップ多い",
  "themeVibe": "驚愕と感動の芸術作品紹介",
  "importedComments": [
    {
      "id": "UgyOxgZCtQNcuLV437p4AaABAg",
      "text": "ずーっと起きてる黒ひげが夢について話すのがなんか良い",
      "author": "@tu_mirai",
      "likeCount": 13730,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T10:26:03Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgyOxgZCtQNcuLV437p4AaABAg.AKTmZKmS4KfAKUN8uHzcuk",
      "text": "寝ないからこそ、醒めないからこそ、夢は終わらないっていう感じいいよね",
      "author": "@azxgd9098",
      "likeCount": 1413,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgyOxgZCtQNcuLV437p4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T15:54:28Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugz6QxeKA5-_-Z-cLWd4AaABAg",
      "text": "このころは黒ひげがちょっと変わった良い奴なイメージだったなぁ…",
      "author": "@ilovesupura-owl",
      "likeCount": 8860,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T02:26:34Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugz6QxeKA5-_-Z-cLWd4AaABAg.AKSvgcVLKR7AKTWPfvKe_K",
      "text": "今も昔も、野望のために執着してるのが好き",
      "author": "@わいやでaaaaa",
      "likeCount": 1219,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "Ugz6QxeKA5-_-Z-cLWd4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T07:56:10Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugz6QxeKA5-_-Z-cLWd4AaABAg.AKSvgcVLKR7AKTfWlYKuSu",
      "text": "海賊らしくていいやん。俺は麦わらのほうがイメージ良くないよ",
      "author": "@dddd4c",
      "likeCount": 614,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "Ugz6QxeKA5-_-Z-cLWd4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T09:24:31Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgwXm9BVVKi6F_KzxwN4AaABAg",
      "text": "ルフィは打撃効かないからいいけど\n巻き込まれたゾロはしっかりダメージ負わされてんのおもろい",
      "author": "@れとろげーまー",
      "likeCount": 4822,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T13:23:40Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgwXm9BVVKi6F_KzxwN4AaABAg.AKU5tQiTiSPAKVc3OewvDf",
      "text": "ベラミーさん、既に武装色を使っていた疑惑",
      "author": "@mama_mama_mama_mama_mama",
      "likeCount": 137,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgwXm9BVVKi6F_KzxwN4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-13T03:32:46Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgwXm9BVVKi6F_KzxwN4AaABAg.AKU5tQiTiSPAKWFgqxOBP1",
      "text": "なにもな゛かった...",
      "author": "@mgpoc",
      "likeCount": 23,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgwXm9BVVKi6F_KzxwN4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-13T09:27:49Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgzSHANZ_1GTQX8Ccvt4AaABAg",
      "text": "黒ひげが「今の戦いはそいつらの勝ちだぜ」って言ってくれるのいいな",
      "author": "@ホロライブとワンピースが好きな男",
      "likeCount": 3444,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-20T01:09:47Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgzSHANZ_1GTQX8Ccvt4AaABAg.AKmOGEokjgyASZ9QgcURTw",
      "text": "黒ひげは普通に倍返ししそう",
      "author": "@石野ブラシ",
      "likeCount": 67,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgzSHANZ_1GTQX8Ccvt4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2026-01-29T08:41:55Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgzSHANZ_1GTQX8Ccvt4AaABAg.AKmOGEokjgyAVUPgmv9fsX",
      "text": "@朝マック-u6d海賊らしくて草",
      "author": "@ミケランジェロ-1",
      "likeCount": 7,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgzSHANZ_1GTQX8Ccvt4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2026-04-12T02:02:03Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgxIwEvCgDD40PpnAUZ4AaABAg",
      "text": "この頃のルフィはふざけてるけど一本の芯がある船長だった…",
      "author": "@マサ-g7u",
      "likeCount": 1507,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T09:11:34Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgxIwEvCgDD40PpnAUZ4AaABAg.AKTe1uGzx4lAKTg04ooNR6",
      "text": "今無いとかエアプでわろた",
      "author": "@いいい-t7g",
      "likeCount": 48,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgxIwEvCgDD40PpnAUZ4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T09:28:47Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "UgxIwEvCgDD40PpnAUZ4AaABAg.AKTe1uGzx4lAKTl9QX-_Dl",
      "text": "@いいい-t7g今あるか…？全くの煽りとかじゃなくてな、この頃の思慮深さとか戦う前の動機とかがどうしても最近子供じみていて読むのがキツくなってきた。エルバフ編は正直途中で読むのを辞めてしまった。",
      "author": "@マサ-g7u",
      "likeCount": 373,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "UgxIwEvCgDD40PpnAUZ4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-07-12T10:13:45Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugw0twsazWPhbhLFiDh4AaABAg",
      "text": "この時期のワンピは間違いなく名作だった",
      "author": "@チャイカツ",
      "likeCount": 1130,
      "isReply": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-10-25T13:17:07Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "Ugw0twsazWPhbhLFiDh4AaABAg.AOhSbF-_4wIAQiFsNJ-OHn",
      "text": "今では神が出てきて、王がぼこぼこにされて、キャラの実力に差があって、昔死んだ奴はインフレに取り残されて雑魚みたいになってるもんな、それでもまぁ面白いから好きだけど",
      "author": "@user-melon-metamo-tapioka",
      "likeCount": 44,
      "isReply": true,
      "parentId": "Ugw0twsazWPhbhLFiDh4AaABAg",
      "publishedAt": "2025-12-14T13:47:53Z"
    },
